Package hc.server.ui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientSession
    a ClientSession instance will be created before ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_MOBILE_LOGIN, and will be released by server after ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_MOBILE_LOGOUT.
    CtrlResponse
    CtrlResponse is used to design a remote controller.
    Dialog
    Dialog is a top-level UI interaction component at center of mobile client.
    HTMLMlet
    HTMLMlet is a UI interaction component, which contains JComponents and present them as HTML (not snapshot) on mobile, you can set CSS for these JComponents.
    MenuItem
    An implementation of an item in a menu.
    Mlet
    Mlet is an instance running in server, and the snapshot of Mlet is presented to mobile.
    ProjectContext
    There is one ProjectContext instance for each HAR Project at runtime.
    ScriptPanel
    ScriptPanel is JComponent to load JavaScript and execute JavaScript on client.
